locality: Tanzania, Kagera, c. 15 km from Bukoba, along the road to the N.
Mafinga, Sao Hill, road Mafinga - Kalinga
South of Mpulungu, SW of Mbala, near Twatasha village
Brooke Bond Tea Estate, ca. 15 km S of Mafinga; 5 km N of Ngwazi House near bottom of hill, in dry, hard-packed, recently burned soil of agricultural field.

Lake Ngwazi Dam end. Brachystegia, Parinari curatifolia stunted woodland with canopy 2 m. tall. With densely vegetated termite mounds with Croton, Apodytes dimidiata, Prunus africana, canopy 4-8 m. tall.
